quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  17,23,"Ndipo Ambuye wako walamula kuti musapembedze wina aliyense koma Iye yekha. Ndipo kuti muwachitire makolo anu zabwino. Ngati wina wa iwo kapena onse akalamba ali kukhala nanu, musawakalipire ayi, koma muziwayankhula ndi mawu aulemu"
  17,24,"Onetsani kudzichepetsa ndi chisoni ndipo munene kuti, “Ambuye wanga! Achitireni chifundo monga momwe iwo adandilerera pamene ine ndidali wamng’ono.”"
  17,25,Ambuye wanu amadziwa kwambiri zonse zimene zili m’mitima mwanu. Ngati muli abwino ndithudi Iye ali wokhululukira kwa anthu amene amadza kwa Iye nthawi zonse modzichepetsa ndi kulapa
  17,26,Ndipo apatseni abale anu ndi anthu ovutika gawo lawo lowayenera ndiponso a paulendo amene avutika. Ndipo musapereke chuma chanu moononga
  17,27,"Ndithudi anthu oononga ndi abale a Satana ndipo Satana, kwa Ambuye wake, ndi wosayamika"
  17,28,"Ndipo ngati iwe siuwathandiza ndipo uli kuyembekezera chisomo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako, yankhula nawo mwachifundo ndi mawu oleza"
  17,29,Ndipo musakhale oumira kapena opereka moononga chifukwa mungadzudzulidwe kapena kukhala osauka kwambiri
  17,30,"Ndithudi Ambuye wako amapereka zambiri kwa aliyense amene wamufuna ndipo amanyalapsa. Ndithudi Iye, kwa akapolo ake, ndi wodziwa ndi woona"
  17,31,Ndipo musawaphe ana anu chifukwa choopa umphawi. Ife timawapatsa zosowa zawo ndi inu nomwe. Ndithudi kuwapha iwo ndi tchimo lalikulu
  17,32,Ndipo musayandikire chigololo. Ndithudi icho ndi chonyansa ndiponso njira yoipa
  17,33,"Ndipo musaphe wina aliyense amene Mulungu waletsa pokhapokha ngati pali chifukwa chololedwa. Ndipo aliyense amene waphedwa mopanda chilungamo, Ife tamupatsa m’bale wake mphamvu zobwezera kapena kukhululuka pa imfa yake. Koma m’bale wakeyo asapyole muyeso pa kubwezeraku. Ndithudi iye ndi wotetezedwa"
  17,34,Ndipo musachiyandikire chuma cha mwana wamasiye kupatula ngati muli ndi cholinga chochisamala mpaka pamene mwini wake adzafike pa msinkhu woti akhoza kuchisamalira yekha. Ndipo kwaniritsani lonjezo lililonse. Ndithudi! mudzafunsidwa za lonjezoli
  17,35,Ndipo kwaniritsani muyeso pamene muyesa zinthu ndipo yesani mwachilungamo polinga zinthu pa sikelo. Zimenezo ndizo zabwino ndipo ndi mapeto abwino kwambiri
  17,36,Ndipo musatsatire zinthu zimene simuzidziwa. Ndithudi kumvera kapena kuyang’ana kapenanso kuganizira kwa mumtima mwa munthu kudzafufuzidwa pa tsiku lachiweruzo
  17,37,"Ndipo musayende modzitukumula pa dziko lapansi, ndithudi, inu simungathe kuboola nthaka ndi kufika kutalika kwa mapiri"
  17,38,Kuipa kwa zonsezi sikukondweretsa Ambuye wako
  17,39,"Ili ndi gawo la luntha limene Ambuye wako wakuuza iwe. Ndipo usatumikire mulungu wina kuonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni chifukwa mwina iwe ungaponyedwe ku Gahena, modzudzulidwa ndi mokankhidwa"
  17,40,Kodi Ambuye wanu wakusankhirani inu ana aamuna ndipo wadzisankhira Iye mwini ana aakazi kuchokera kwa Angelo? Ndithudi! Inu mukuyankhula mawu oopsa
  17,41,"Ndithudi Ife tafotokoza chinthu chilichonse m’Korani iyi kuti iwo achenjezedwe, koma iyo siili kuonjezera chilichonse koma kuipidwa"
  17,42,"Nena, “Kukadakhala kuti kuli milungu ina yoonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, monga momwe akunenera, iyo ikadapeza njira yoti ikhale pafupi ndi Mulungu.”"
  17,43,"Kuyamikidwa ndi kukhala pamwamba, kukhale kwake! Kuchokera ku bodza lalikulu limene iwo ali nkunena"
  17,44,"Miyamba isanu ndi iwiri, dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zimakhala m’menemo zimamulemekeza Iye ndipo palibe chinthu chomwe sichimulemekeza Mulungu. Koma inu simumva mayamiko. Ndithudi Iye ndi woleza mtima ndipo ndi wokhululukira nthawi zonse"
  17,45,"Pamene iwe umawerenga Korani, Ife timaika, pakati pa iwe ndi iwo amene sakhulupirira za moyo umene uli nkudza tchingo losaoneka"
  17,46,Ndipo Ife taika zophimba m’mitima mwawo kuti mwina angaizindikire ndi m’makutu mwawo kuti asaimvetse. Ndipo pamene iwe utchula Ambuye wako yekha mu Korani iwo amatembenuka kuthawa mosangalala
  17,47,"Ife timadziwa kwambiri zimene iwo akumva ndi pamene amamvetsera kwa iwe. Ndipo pamene amanong’onezana, taona anthu oipa, amanena kuti: “Inu mukutsatira munthu wolodzedwa.”"
  17,48,Taona mmene akuperekera zitsanzo zokhudza iwe. Motero iwo asochera ndipo sangathe kupeza njira
  17,49,"Ndipo iwo amati, “Kodi pamene ife tidzasanduka mafupa ndi zidutswa zopereseka kodi tidzaukitsidwanso kukhala chilengedwe chatsopano?”"